<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n04152g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n04" href="#n04152g">N04 (VI.B.25)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n04all.htm#n04152g"> 152(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> a latere / in petto </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: L. <i>A latere</i>: from the side. <font color="green">[The term is usually applied to a particular type of papal legate, a cleric sent on a mission by the Pope as his personal representative. See <a name="n12134k" href="n12all.htm#n12134k">N12 (VI.B.14):134(k)</a>. ]</font> It. <i>In petto</i>: in the breast, in the heart. At times the Pope declares that in addition to those whom he has publicly made cardinals, he has made one or more others whose names he reserves <i>in petto</i>. When these are subsequently made known, they take rank from the date of their original nomination. </mm> </dd></dl>
